\c 2
\s Vanhu ngavatsvake Jehovha kutonga kuchigere kusvika
\p
\v 1 Unganai, zvirokwazvo unganai, imwi rudzi rusinganyari;
\v 2 chirevo chisati chabereka, zuva risati rapfuura sehundi, kutsamwa kukuru kwaJehovha kusati kwauya pamusoro penyu, zuva rokutsamwa kwaJehovha risati rauya pamusoro penyu.
\v 3 Tsvakai Jehovha, imwi mose vanyoro venyika, imwi makachengeta mitemo yake; tsvakai kururama, tsvakai unyoro; zvimwe mungavanzika nezuva rokutsamwa kwaJehovha.
\p
\v 4 nekuti Gaza richasiiwa, Ashikeroni richaitwa dongo; vachadzinga Ashidhodhi masikati makuru, Ekironi richadzurwa.
\v 5 Vane nhamo vagere panyika iri pagungwa, irwo rudzi rwavaKeteti! Shoko raJehovha rinokutuka, iwe Kenani, nyika yavaFirisitia; ndichakuparadza, kuti parege kuzova anogarapo.
\v 6 mahombekombe egungwa aichava mafuro anamapako avafudzi nezvirugu zvamakwai.
\v 7 Mahombekombe achava evakasara veimba yaJudha; vachafudzapo makwai avo; vacharara pasi madekwani mudzimba dzeAshikeroni; nekuti Jehovha Mwari wavo achavashanyira nokudzosa kutapwa kwavo.
\p
\v 8 Ndakanzwa kuzvidzwa kwaMoabhi, nokutuka kwavana vaAmoni, kwavakazvidza nako vanhu vangu, vachiita manyawi pamuganhu wavo.
\v 9 Naizvozvo noupenyu hwangu ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo, Mwari walsiraeri, Zvirokwazvo, Moabhi vachaita seSodhoma, navana vaAmoni seGomora, nyika yorukato, namakomba omunyu, namatongo nokusingaperi; vanhu vangu vakasara vachavaita chinhu chakatapwa, vakasara vorudzi rwangu vachavagara nhaka.
\p
\v 10 Ndizvo zvavachapiwa nokuda kokuzvikudza kwavo, nekuti vakazvidza vanhu vaJehovha wehondo nokuzvikudza kwavari.
\v 11 Jehovha achavatyisa kwazvo, nekuti achaparadza vamwari vose venyika; vanhu vachamunamata iye, umwe  neumwe   achibva panzvimbo yake, naizvo zviwi zvose zvendudzi.
\p
\v 12 Nemiwo veItiopia, muchaurawa nomunondo wangu.
\v 13 Achatambanudzira ruoko rwake kurutivi rwokumusoro, ndokuparadza Asiriya; Ninivhe achariita dongo, riome serenje.
\v 14 Zvipfuwo zvicharara pasi mukati maro, idzo mhuka dzamarudzi ose; hukurwizi nenungu zvicharara pamisoro yembiru dzaro; izwi rokurira kwazvo richanzwika pamahwindo; kuparadzwa kuchavapo pazvikumbaridzo, nekuti wakafukunura zvakavezwa zvemisidhari.
\v 15 Iri ndiro guta raigara nomufaro risina hanya, raiti mumwoyo maro, Ndini, hakuchino umwe  kunze kwangu! Haiwa, raitwa dongo sei, nzvimbo inorara mhuka! umwe  neumwe   anopfuura napo acharidza muridzo, achizunungusa ruoko rwake.
